2026-05-09T21:33:21.5417586Z 22    <!--
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5418122Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5418818Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5419484Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5420272Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5421044Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5421826Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5422789Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5423579Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5424630Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5425370Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-09T21:33:21.5425934Z 33    -->
